name: Scenario
tagline: What If Scenario based app.  Have fun playing with your family or friends.
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
A fun app, "What If scenario" based questions.  The App displays next "What If" question and beeps when button is pressed.  The user also have the option to shake the phone to display next question.  Enjoy!!.
